While not the largest flash modifier on the market, this is easily one of the most compact and well built that I’ve come across. The compact design and small carry case keeps you mobile will offering a good diffusion solution to your off-camera lighting set up. The hotshoe flash mounts outside of the rapid box so you can easily access the flash controls, or use a line-of-sight triggering method if you prefer.
